extractParameters

protected void extractParameters(String parameters)
                          throws IllegalFormatException
This extracts the parameters from a line that comes from typelib. Sample lines looks like: 
 INVOKE_FUNC;VT_VOID ;SetRange;[{in-}VT_I4 Start,{in-}VT_I4 End]
 INVOKE_FUNC;VT_VOID ;Collapse;[{in-optional-}VT_VARIANT Direction]
 INVOKE_FUNC;VT_VOID ;Sync;[MsoSyncEventType SyncEventType]
The parameters section for the first one would be [{in-}VT_I4 Start,{in-}VT_I4 End] where the first parameter is {in-}VT_I4 Start and the second parameter is {in-}VT_I4 End

parameters -
Throws:
IllegalFormatException
